Class InputFieldsTableModel

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      reqsimile.data.InputFieldsTableModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
public class InputFieldsTableModel
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel

InputFieldsTableModel is the table model for the tables in the settings dialog used for selecting which fields that are to be displayed in the summary and detail views, and be used for calculation.

Since:
1.4.2
